Medvedev Clears U.S. Troops to Fly Over Russia to Afghanistan

-- B y   S c o t t   R o s e
-- 
2011-03-09T16:50:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/medvedev-clears-u-s-troops-to-fly-over-russia-to-afghanistan.html
President  Dmitry Medvedev  approved
an agreement letting the U.S. fly weapons and troops over  Russia 
for “efforts to provide security, stabilize and rebuild”  Afghanistan .  Medvedev signed the measure today after lawmakers gave
final approval on March 2, the Kremlin said in an e-mailed
statement from Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Scott Rose in  London  at 
 rrose10@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Willy Morris at   wmorris@bloomberg.net . 